{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"827a3ab5e3","title":"防敌从元山登陆","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"13a5d87791","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":13,"articleId":"827a3ab5e3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"2fc32c5aa2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"4d2fd71af0","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1951年4月10日24时彭德怀关于第五次战役部署给毛泽东的电报。电报说：我作战企图，拟从金化至加平线，利用这一带大山区赞开一个缺口，将敌人东西割裂，然后用第九兵团和第十九兵团对西线敌人进行战役两翼迁回，第三兵团正面攻击，以各个分割歼灭敌人。力求在三八线北歼灭敌人几个师，得手后再向纵深发展。攻击时间，如敌进展快，我拟4月20日前后开始，各兵团4月15日可集结完毕，时间较仓促些；如故进展不快时，待5月上句出击。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8e572d75f8","type":"title","text":"防敌从元山登陆","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3"},{"id":"2fc32c5aa2","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3"},{"id":"4d2fd71af0","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十日廿四时电悉。（一）完全同意你的预定部署，望依情况坚决执行之。（二）为防敌从元山登陆，似须以四十二军主力位于元山城内及其附近，确保元山，请的定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3"},{"id":"06ff5642d0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3"},{"id":"2135c256d3","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3"}],"page":{"id":"95e39b6c44","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"827a3ab5e3","start":234,"end":234}}}},"__N_SSG":true}